<body>
<div><head>《發蒙記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.2">甘棗令人不惑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.3">萱草可以忘憂。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.4">徐堅《初學記》卷二十七、《太平御覽》卷九百九十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.5">西域有火鼠之布，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.6">東海有不灰之木。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.7">《初學記》卷二十九、《太平御覽》卷九百十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.8">廉頗年老，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.9">日噉肉百斤。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-1a.10">虞世南《北堂書鈔》卷一百四十三、《太平御覽》卷八百四十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.2">蠅生積灰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.3">蜂出蜘蛛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.4">腐木為螢火，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.5">蠐螬生朽芻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.6">《太平御覽》卷九百四十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.7">師子五色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.8">而食虎於巨木之岫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.9">一噬則自人仆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.10">唯畏鉤戟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-2a.11">《太平御覽》卷三百五十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.2">玉精名委，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.3">似美女而青衣見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.4">以桃戟刺之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.5">以其名呼之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.6">可得也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.7">《太平御覽》卷三百五十二引《啟蒙記》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.8">茲依陶宗儀《說郛》本錄之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.9">虎以狗為酒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.10">雞以蜈蚣為酒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.11">鳩以桑椹為酒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.12">貓以薄荷為酒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.13">蛇以茱萸為酒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-3a.14">謂食之即醉也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a.2">東方朔乃太白星精。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a.3">水行峽路最險，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a.4">以艷澦為則。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a.5">萬歲蟾蜍頭上有角，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-4a.6">頷下有丹書八字。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.2">琴以七寶飾之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.3">名璠璵之樂。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.4">子路感雷精而生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.5">尚剛好勇。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.6">秦始皇決事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.7">縣石之一。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.8">縣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.9">稱也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-5a.10">石百二十斤。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.2">漢武所生之殿曰猗蘭。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.3">蒙恬之為筆也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.4">柘木為管，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.5">鹿毛為柱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.6">羊毛為被。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.7">並《說郛》本。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.8">自「虎以狗為酒」已下九節，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-6a.9">依陶氏錄之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.2">侯官謝端曾於海中得一大螺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.3">中有美女，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.4">云我天漢中白水素女，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.5">天矜卿貧，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.6">令我為卿妻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.7">《初學記》卷八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.8">醜男鬷蔑。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-7a.9">《初學記》卷十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.2">醜女離春。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.3">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.4">伯益作舟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.5">《初學記》卷二十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.6">駃騠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.7">刳其母腹而生。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-8a.8">《史記‧匈奴列傳》司馬貞《索隱》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.2">鼈二足曰能。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.3">《史記‧夏本紀》張守節《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.4">青蚨可以還錢。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.5">《後漢書‧郡國志》劉昭《注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.6">治戶傷孕婦。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-9a.7">《太平御覽》卷一百八十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.2">獺以猨為婦。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.3">《埤雅‧釋獸》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.4">詁娚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.5">《集韻》平聲下二十七咸諵喃娚注。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.6">尼咸切，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.7">詁諵語聲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.8">或作「喃」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1526_CHANT_001-10a.9">束晳作「娚」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
